Contact Us.

Need a hand? We can help. Contact us at 1-800-ALLSTATE (1-800-255-7828) 24 hours a day, seven days a week. You can also find an agent or email us. 


Allstate's headquarters are located at: 
2775 Sanders Road
Northbrook, IL 60062
