        10/18/2013
    

I have been with allstate for a long time. I generally call them for payment purpose and have been a good customer to them. But when I called them to inform them about removing a car from policy, they informed that they will prorate the amount and return me the rest of the policy money for the car. They promised they will follow up with an email which never happened. Its always that case with this agency. Finally I called again and I was informed that they will pay me some amount of money because my insurance increased to the other vehicles in that policy. I had to finally call them to cancel my policy. I went to get a quote from another insurance and its way to less than allstate.Finally I wanted to talk to the management and I did not get any call from them.. Thats it - Good bye Allstate for the Mayhem you had created.




