I have enjoyed working with Cathy over the years.  She is friendly and knowledgeable.  After a minor accident she took the time to explain the process of getting the car fixed and back on the road. Very motivated and easy to work with.  An outstanding agent.







I've been with Cathy for a little over a year and I am so happy I've had the opportunity to do business with her.  When I purchased my first car, she was very helpful through the entire process and was able to explain to me all my paper work, since insurance is a foreign language to me.

What I love about Cathy is her exuberant personality.  I love dropping off my monthly check for my insurance payment to sit down with her and chit chat.  She truly cares about her clients and she remembers each and every person- you are not treated like you are a number or commission.  She is very professional.  Her assistant is also very personable and the two compliment one another to have a success business.  

As for the other post that was so negative, I wanted to inform you, her sign informs you that she is available by appointment only on Saturdays.







Specifically came to this Allstate office owned by Cathy Nguyen since their website said they'd be open on Sat morning. If your website says you are open and so does the info on your office window, you better be open during those promised times.  Showed up there - ghost town.

Bottom line: Lame. Update your freakin website.







I have been with Cathy since I was 16 and could drive. The staff in the office is very friendly and will explain and guide you through all paperwork. They make the policy very understandable. I had an car accident and Cathy guided me through the whole process which made it stress free. As for price, ask for student discount if you have over a 3.0 gpa.







Cathy Nguyen is an awesome agent, very friendly, helpful, and on top of everything. Whenever I had a question or request, she responded within the hour.  Thanks Cathy for your great service!







My family has used Kathy's service for over 23 years. We started with car insurance when we just moved here. We then added our home insurance and now all the cars for our children who weren't even born when we signed up with her. I have used other ibsurance agents and will go on record to say Kathy is the best. I saw a lot of letters from other companies promising better deals if we move. But I have never tempted because Kathy is so awesome. Some example:  She told us when renting cars, we do not need to get collision insurance because our umbrella will cover that. That saves us lots of money over the last 25+ years.  She told us about free towing Servixes we get with All State and sent us the cards for that. Once my son car was towed while in college and he couldn't get it out of the towing company because his name was not on the registration; only his dad name was on there and dad was out of the country.  We could wait for his dad to get back but that meant paying $80/day extra. In desperation, I called Cathy and she showed me how to addmy son's name to the registration. We were able to fix that without incurring additional cost. She and her staffs are awesome. They are ALWAYS there to pick up the phone during business hours. They are always pleasant, professional and have answers to all my questions. They are the best. You should use Cathy's agency if you need any insurance services. She is the best.







